HOW TO BEGIN THE READING

‚úî Open a file from your device or sd-card using built-in file manager.
Formats: FB2, EPUB (no DRM) / KEPUB, TXT, HTML + reading books in ZIP-archives.
‚úî Send a web page from your favorite web browser, Pocket, Feedly, Evernote;
‚úî Use Reedy for opening books from another apps and clouds (Google Drive, Dropbox, etc.);
‚úî Copy any text or link and paste it into the reader.
Also you can simply share it with Reedy.


